close_reason: Completed planned scope for Pi wrapper fallback path hardening and preserved verification context for future changes.
body: "Context: docs/pi/extensions/pm/index.ts currently falls back to node dist/cli.js when pm is unavailable, which assumes the current working directory is the repository root. Approach: resolve fallback CLI path from module location and add targeted regression tests for deterministic fallback arg shape."
